articles.title: Kris Jenner Shares She Has a Tumor in Kardashians Trailer - E! NEWS
articles.description: Kris Jenner shares a scary medical update in the trailer for season five of The Kardashians.
articles.content:
Kris Jenner is opening up about a health scare.
In The Kardashians season five trailer, released May 8, the family matriarch shares the results from her recent medical appointment with her daughters… [+727 chars]
